No. 20,

Misc.

Billie et al., General Council, Miccosukee Seminole Nation, v. Seminole Indians of Florida. Morton H. Silver for petitioners. Guy Martin for respondent. Solicitor General Rankin, Assistant Attorney General Morton and Roger P. Marquis filed a memorandum for the United States.

Court of Claims. Certiorari denied.
